Rosewind Corp.


                  Rosewind Corp. operates offshore sailing school. Its curriculum consists of a fast track experience for up to two student sailors who voyage for a week or more and topics include marine environment and safety at sea, life rafts and ditch bags, medical preparedness and fist aid, features of offshore capable vessels, rigging and deck gear and other. Rosewind was founded on August 9, 2002 and is headquartered in Loveland, CO.                




