Vyrix Pharmaceuticals, Inc.


                  Vyrix Pharmaceuticals, Inc. operates as a clinical-stage biopharmaceutical company. It maximizes the clinical and commercial potential of its late-stage sexual dysfunction products. The company is currently focused on advancing the development of Zertane™ for Premature Ejaculation (PE) in the US and around the world. Vyrix Pharmaceuticals was founded on November 18, 2013 and is headquartered in Greenwood Village, CO.                




